name: TALK
description: The concept TALK from the corresponding album by the alternative music project whoiswelanski consists of over 11 minutes of music. 4 Songs named T, A, L and K (all available as NFTs on Hicetnunc) that can be listened to in one piece due to the smooth transitions in between the songs and that describe a person feeling lost because of not swinging on the same wave of communication with other people.
